title: USA freestyle skier Kiernan Fagan and a luge ride with Tobi Jizzle at Lausanne 2020
description: We find out what trick Kiernan Fagan would love to land at the Winter Youth Olympic Games. Plus, we sent influencer Tobi Jizzle down a luge and tested his Olympic knowledge at the same time.
